  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess antiviral activity when administered alone for 3 days
      or in combination with peginterferon and ribavirin for 12 weeks. This study will also
      evaluate the safety and tolerability of treatment with VCH-222 when given alone or in
      combination with peginterferon and ribavirin.

      The study will also evaluate the pharmacokinetic profile of VCH-222 in HCV infected subjects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
